AIR
CALIFORNIA
TIMETABLE
Effective October 1, 1978
New: Statewide Service to Fresno
SERVING FRESNO, LAKE TAHOE, MONTEREY/SALINAS
OAKLAND, ONTARIO, ORANGE COUNTY, PALM SPRINGS,
SACRAMENTO, SAN DIEGO, SAN FRANCISCO AND SAN JOSE.

Fresno.
Now Air California
makes it easy.
Statewide service and the lowest fares to Central California's
gateway city.
Fresno is the gateway to agriculture, business and recreation
in Central California. And now only Air California can jet you
nonstop between Fresno and Oakland, Ontario, Orange
County, San Jose and Lake Tahoe, with convenient
connecting service between
San Diego, Sacramento and
Palm Springs.
Flying Air California to
Fresno is quick and
economical, with regulary
scheduled morning and
evening flights.
Air California makes flying
to Fresno easy, with
computerized reservations
and ticketing and the
lowest fares.
So plan to take off for
Fresno on Air California
And make it easy on yourself.
